<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.400095>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. A map of the Yilgarn region of Western Australia and the sampled calcrete aquifers (black) with their position in the palaeodrainages (grey shading) including Carey, Nabberu and Raeside. Numbers for calcretes and non-calcrete areas include: 1, Sturt Meadows (SM); 2, Cunyu (CUN); 3, Lake Miranda East (LME); 4, Lake Miranda West (LMW); 5, Halfpenny Well (HAW); 6, Nambi (NAM); 7, Laverton Downs Windarra (LDW); 8, Mt Morgans (MOR); 9, Goosberry Hill, Wooroloo (WOO); 10, Wongalinga Beach, Qld." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/400095/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

